          { id: "s2", title: "Module Assessment", content: "You will receive a 60-minute scenario-based assessment. You must score 80% or above to unlock the SOC Operator track. Your response will be AI-reviewed within 24 hours, then signed off by a human supervisor. Do not use AI tools to write your response — your submission is your own work. Submissions are checked for AI-generated content and will be rejected if detected." }
